         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">… all crystal jewels will be in ditches. The beryll-coloured …</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>665</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">… he will be a cakravartin king, lord over the four worlds …</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>665</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a5"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:hackstein1995"/><citedRange>98</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">… the glorious and the beautiful will conquer … because of [their] worth …</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>666</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a7"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">… will sit; brilliant will be the earth …</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>666</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">… will cover all …</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>666</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b5"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:hackstein1995"/><citedRange>250</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... sehen einander in den lieblichen Gärten.</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">... see one another in the lovely gardens.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>322</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b7"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">… on that spot there will be a city with the name Ṛddhi (?), vaiśra…</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>666</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
